---
title: Mumbai-Spiced Beef, Bean & Kumara Dosa-Dillas  with Charred Corn Salsa & Yoghurt
description: These chunky, beef-packed dosa-dillas are the ultimate ruler of the dinner table. So bow down to the might of the roasted kumara and cannellini beans, cooked in rich spices and accompanied by a charred corn salsa. Long may this tasty dish reign.
We’ve replaced the lentils in this recipe with cannellini beans due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!
